  <title>Xbitmaps-&xbitmaps-version;</title>

  <indexterm zone="xbitmaps">
    <primary sortas="a-xbitmaps">Luit</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <para>Xbitmaps provides static graphics needed by xorg applications to 
  draw screen elements.</para>

